tokens.description: Welcome to Machiniverse ! Machinies are a collection of 8,888 units of machine forever run on Ethereum Blockchain. Which acts as your representative of being active for 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. Owning Machinies in your wallet does not only to keep you on the move but grants ownership privilege.
